data.description: Beautiful 2 story home in the popular Davis Ridge community. Setting on a corner lot, this home features an open foyer, formal dining room, study and a kitchen that is open to the great room. Perfect for entertaining. Seller has finished their renovations including new kitchen and bath cabinets with granite tops and new faucets. New garage door.  LVP flooring throughout the home.  Large primary suite with soaking tub, a large bonus room with window seat.
